{"id":4253,"date":"2025-06-16T16:56:14","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T09:56:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4253"},"modified":"2025-06-16T16:56:14","modified_gmt":"2025-06-16T09:56:14","slug":"kem-chong-nang-pho-rong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/kem-chong-nang-pho-rong\/","title":{"rendered":"Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec? B\u00ed quy\u1ebft ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 bao gi\u1edd b\u0103n kho\u0103n <\/span><\/i><b><i>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> v\u00e0 v\u00ec sao l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y ch\u01b0a? Tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n nay c\u00f3 v\u00f4 v\u00e0n lo\u1ea1i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u00f2ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n. Khi hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u nguy c\u01a1 ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng, l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm v\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 ung th\u01b0 da.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"kem-chong-nang-pho-rong-la-gi\"><\/span><b>Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c tia UV bao g\u1ed3m UVA v\u00e0 UVB l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u00e1nh m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi. Tia UVA x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp s\u00e2u, l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, g\u00e2y n\u00e1m, t\u00e0n nhang v\u00e0 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, tia UVB t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean l\u1edbp bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec, khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecfng r\u00e1t, bong tr\u00f3c v\u00e0 t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh ung th\u01b0 bi\u1ec3u m\u00f4 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u1ea3 hai lo\u1ea1i tia tr\u00ean. Lo\u1ea1i kem n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e1n nh\u00e3n \u201cBroad Spectrum\u201d ho\u1eb7c \u201cUVA\/UVB Protection\u201d v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF t\u1eeb 30 tr\u1edf l\u00ean, k\u00e8m theo PA+++ ho\u1eb7c cao h\u01a1n, gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u00f3 h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-nhan-biet-kem-chong-nang-pho-rong-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4254\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4254\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4254\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-1.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4254\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF: B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi tia UVB. N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn SPF t\u1eeb 30 tr\u1edf l\u00ean cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 d\u00e0i l\u00e2u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 PA: Ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng tia UVA. C\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u201c+\u201d th\u00ec m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u00e0ng cao.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00f4ng tin nh\u00e3n m\u00e1c: C\u00e1c c\u1ee5m t\u1eeb nh\u01b0 \u201cBroad Spectrum\u201d, \u201cFull Spectrum\u201d, \u201cUVA\/UVB Shield\u201d th\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean bao b\u00ec c\u1ee7a kem ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ho\u1ea1t t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 k\u1ebdm oxit ho\u1eb7c titan dioxide th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, \u00edt g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"loi-ich-khi-dung-kem-chong-nang-pho-rong-moi-ngay\"><\/span><b>L\u1ee3i \u00edch khi d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ngan-chan-tac-dong-tu-anh-sang-xanh-hev\"><\/span><b><i>Ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh (HEV)<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tia UV m\u00e0 <\/span><b>\u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u1eeb c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, laptop c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a. Tia HEV th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9 s\u0103n ch\u1eafc c\u1ee7a da. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ed1ng HEV nh\u1eb1m ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u, nh\u0103n nheo do ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-ve-khoi-uva-%e2%80%93-%e2%80%9cke-giet-tham-lang%e2%80%9d-cua-lan-da\"><\/span><b><i>B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 kh\u1ecfi UVA \u2013 &#8220;k\u1ebb gi\u1ebft th\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng&#8221; c\u1ee7a l\u00e0n da<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tia UVA ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, quanh n\u0103m v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb c\u1ea3n b\u1edfi k\u00ednh ho\u1eb7c m\u00e2y m\u00f9. Ch\u00fang ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 collagen, elastin v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da l\u00e3o h\u00f3a nhanh ch\u00f3ng. Nh\u1edd v\u00e0o c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kho\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 zinc oxide, kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n UVA x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp s\u00e2u v\u00e0o l\u1edbp h\u1ea1 b\u00ec \u2013 v\u00f9ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4255\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4255\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4255\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-2.webp\" alt=\"L\u1ee3i \u00edch khi d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4255\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">L\u1ee3i \u00edch khi d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chong-lai-tia-uvb-%e2%80%93-thu-pham-gay-chay-nang-va-bong-rat\"><\/span><b><i>Ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i tia UVB \u2013 th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m g\u00e2y ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng v\u00e0 b\u1ecfng r\u00e1t<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tia UVB ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0a v\u00e0 g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da. V\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng, da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 kh\u1ecfi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t, s\u1ea1m m\u00e0u v\u00e0 nguy c\u01a1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ung th\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thanh-phan-thuong-gap-trong-kem-chong-nang-pho-rong\"><\/span><b><i>Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Zinc Oxide (K\u1ebdm oxit): C\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 tia UVA, UVB v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da m\u1ee5n ho\u1eb7c nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Titanium Dioxide: T\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c ng\u0103n tia UVB v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n tia UVA, \u00edt g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng trong s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m cho tr\u1ebb em.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u00f2ng c\u00f2n b\u1ed5 sung niacinamide, vitamin C, vitamin E, hyaluronic acid, ceramide&#8230; \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o \u1ea9m.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"loi-khuyen-su-dung-hieu-qua-kem-chong-nang\"><\/span><b><i>L\u1eddi khuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 trong nh\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c khi tr\u1eddi \u00e2m u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thoa kem tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra ngo\u00e0i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 15\u201320 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thoa l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed7i 2 ti\u1ebfng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1eebng b\u1ecf qu\u00ean nh\u1eefng v\u00f9ng da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m nh\u01b0 c\u1ed5, tai, g\u00e1y \u2013 n\u01a1i d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb tia UV t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4256\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4256\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4256\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-3.webp\" alt=\"L\u1eddi khuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/71-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4256\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">L\u1eddi khuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-ket\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft:<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng cho th\u1eafc m\u1eafc <\/span><b>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m khi\u00ean b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi m\u1ecdi nguy c\u01a1 t\u1eeb \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed. \u0110\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap da \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec v\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i tr\u1ebb trung l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean thoa kem m\u1ed7i s\u00e1ng \u2013 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft da \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 bao gi\u1edd b\u0103n kho\u0103n kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 v\u00ec sao l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y ch\u01b0a?<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4257,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4253","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4253","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4253"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4253\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4258,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4253\/revisions\/4258"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4257"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4253"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4253"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4253"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}